Follow these steps if you have an active website. The platform will analyze it to automatically enrich your business configuration.

---

## Step 1: Start the Setup

From the main dashboard, click **Continue** on the **"Set up your business"** step.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Home screen - Continue button */}

---

## Step 2: Business Type and Category

Select whether your business sells **Products** or **Services**, then choose your category or niche (e.g., supplements, sportswear, food).

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Business type selection */}

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Category or niche selection */}

Click **Continue**.

---

## Step 3: Enter Your Website

Type your website URL. The platform will analyze it to better understand your business.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Field to enter the website URL */}

Click **Continue**.

---

## Step 4: Record Your Business Audio

The platform guides you with specific questions. Answer each one by recording your voice naturally.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Main audio screen with guided questions */}

### What does your business do?
Explain what your business does and what type of product or service you offer.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Question - What does your business do? */}

> *Example: "We are a company that sells high-quality sports supplements for athletes and active people."*

### Who buys from you?
Describe your ideal customer: who they are, what they're looking for, what they need.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Question - Who buys from you? */}

> *Example: "Young athletes between 20 and 35 years old who are looking for performance and muscle recovery."*

### What do they say about you?
Share what your customers usually say about your business, product, or service.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Question - What do they say about you? */}

> *Example: "They love the quality of the products and the fast shipping."*

### Price and margin
Indicate your average selling price and approximate profit margin.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Price and margin question */}

> *Example: "The average price is $80. The margin is 40%."*

When you finish all the questions, click **Continue**.

<Callout type="info" title="Tip">
  Speak naturally. The more specific you are, the more accurate your campaigns will be.
</Callout>

---

## Step 5: Add Your Products

Upload the products you want to advertise. For each one:

1. **Photo** — click the image area and select a photo from your computer
2. **Name** — the product name
3. **Description** — main benefits or features
4. **Price** — retail selling price
5. **Margin** — profit percentage

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Product form with all fields */}

Click **Save** and repeat for each additional product.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: List with saved products */}

<Callout type="info" title="How many products to add?">
  Start with your 2 or 3 best-selling products. You can add more at any time.
</Callout>

When done, click **Continue**.

---

## Step 6: Brand & Identity

Define your brand's visual identity so that your ads are consistent with your business.

### Logo
Upload your business logo (PNG or JPG with a transparent background recommended). The name is detected automatically.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Logo upload area */}

### Brand Color
Accept the automatically detected color or enter a custom hexadecimal code.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Brand color picker */}

### Communication Styles
Select the adjectives that represent your brand. Remove the ones that don't fit.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Style selection */}

### Prohibited Words
Enter words you **don't** want to appear in your ads.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Prohibited words field */}

Click **Continue**.

---

## Step 7: Ideal Customer

The AI pre-detects your customer profile from the audio. Review and edit if needed.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Ideal customer screen with pre-detected fields */}

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Description** | Who your ideal customer is |
| **Location** | Where your customers are (city, region, or country) |
| **Problem you solve** | The main need your business addresses |

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Location and problem fields */}

Click **Save** on each edited field, then click **Continue**.

<Callout type="info" title="Tip">
  Be specific about the problem: instead of "lack of time", write "lack of time to prepare healthy meals".
</Callout>

---

## Step 8: AI Diagnosis

The platform analyzes all your information (including your website and Instagram if connected) and detects:

- **Main pain points** of your audience
- **Recommendations** to improve your brand communication

{/* 📸 Screenshot: AI diagnosis screen with results */}

---

## Step 9: Finish

Click **Finish**. Your business is now ready to create strategies and launch campaigns.

{/* 📸 Screenshot: Confirmation screen - setup complete */}

### Summary
- ✅ Business type and category
- ✅ Website connected
- ✅ Business audio
- ✅ Products
- ✅ Brand & identity
- ✅ Ideal customer
- ✅ AI diagnosis completed

